title: Bill Caswell and DIY Motorsports -- /ROAD TESTAMENT
description: Bill Caswell "quit his life" to compete against pro drivers at Rally Mexico in a $500 Craigslist BMW. Caswell joins Road Testament to talk DIY motorsports and the upcoming Paramount Pictures film about his life story of epic hoonage on a shoestring.
